WEBVTT

00:00:17.684 --> 00:00:18.977
Why

00:00:20.895 --> 00:00:22.814
Do you resent Father?

00:00:26.609 --> 00:00:28.278
You killed Prince Yeongan

00:00:29.529 --> 00:00:32.073
And now seek to harm even Father. Why?

00:00:32.574 --> 00:00:33.700
Look closely.

00:00:37.495 --> 00:00:38.580
See

00:00:40.582 --> 00:00:42.834
How I came to die.

00:00:54.721 --> 00:00:57.724
Father poisoned me.

00:01:04.022 --> 00:01:05.732
Father

00:01:07.734 --> 00:01:08.568
Killed me.

00:01:10.862 --> 00:01:13.656
- Your Majesty, you are awake! - Your Majesty.

00:01:20.371 --> 00:01:22.499
- Chief Eunuch Kim. - Yes, Your Majesty.

00:01:22.582 --> 00:01:24.709
Summon the Chief Royal Secretary.

00:01:27.337 --> 00:01:28.171
Your Majesty.

00:01:31.091 --> 00:01:32.383
There is no time.

00:01:35.011 --> 00:01:39.432
The pestilence must be contained at once. Carry out the edict as it is written.

00:01:43.937 --> 00:01:44.979
Your Majesty.

00:01:45.063 --> 00:01:48.858
Are you ordering us to kill everyone in the village?

00:01:48.942 --> 00:01:51.277
PUT THEM ALL TO DEATH

00:01:53.530 --> 00:01:55.073
Do not delay.

00:01:56.324 --> 00:01:58.076
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:02.205
<i>A living ak-gwi.</i>

00:02:03.748 --> 00:02:05.875
Father killed me.

00:02:07.418 --> 00:02:10.672
Father killed me when I learned of his sins.

00:02:18.596 --> 00:02:22.600
Since you know the secret as well, he will kill you.

00:02:23.393 --> 00:02:24.894
- I am next. - You are next.

00:02:24.978 --> 00:02:29.774
You know the secret. Father killed me. Father poisoned me. You are next.

00:02:29.858 --> 00:02:32.068
- He will kill me too. - He will kill you soon.

00:02:33.570 --> 00:02:35.697
- You know the secret. - Because I know the truth as well.

00:02:35.780 --> 00:02:37.699
Father killed everyone.

00:02:39.117 --> 00:02:42.745
THE EAST PALACE

00:02:42.829 --> 00:02:44.747
<i>You are next.</i>

00:03:01.806 --> 00:03:03.266
Damn it.

00:03:04.475 --> 00:03:06.644
Even here, I still cannot see clearly.

00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:52.023
Princess.

00:04:07.372 --> 00:04:10.333
You defied my order to save Prince Yeongan.

00:04:10.833 --> 00:04:14.379
And yet you hid here, deceiving me

00:04:15.255 --> 00:04:17.340
And taking me for a fool?

00:04:17.423 --> 00:04:20.426
That is how I saved Your Majesty from the spirit.

00:04:20.510 --> 00:04:23.137
I heard you even dug up the body of the Crown Prince.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.973
Where is the body now?

00:04:25.056 --> 00:04:27.308
I cannot tell you.

00:04:27.809 --> 00:04:31.145
It is necessary to banish the spirit.

00:04:31.229 --> 00:04:32.272
For that spirit is

00:04:32.855 --> 00:04:34.565
Your son, Your Majesty.

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.571
You have ten days.

00:04:41.406 --> 00:04:44.284
- Banish the spirit within that time. - Ten days are not enough.

00:04:44.367 --> 00:04:45.451
I said ten days.

00:04:45.535 --> 00:04:49.080
Then you must do as I say as well, Your Majesty.

00:04:49.163 --> 00:04:50.915
Mind your tongue. How dare you--

00:04:50.999 --> 00:04:53.918
I will place a ward in your bedchamber.

00:04:54.002 --> 00:04:56.296
It is to keep the spirit from entering.

00:04:56.879 --> 00:04:58.798
Unless you wish to cough up blood

00:05:00.008 --> 00:05:02.677
And be at death's door again.

00:05:15.189 --> 00:05:16.441
Very well.

00:05:17.025 --> 00:05:17.900
On one condition.

00:05:19.527 --> 00:05:21.738
Place it outside the palace hall.

00:05:56.481 --> 00:05:57.315
Princess.

00:05:59.192 --> 00:06:00.193
Princess.

00:06:02.570 --> 00:06:04.655
Princess!

00:06:07.492 --> 00:06:08.576
It cannot be

00:06:12.747 --> 00:06:14.832
Princess, are you all right?

00:06:27.553 --> 00:06:28.554
Are you awake?

00:06:35.978 --> 00:06:37.563
What happened?

00:06:38.439 --> 00:06:39.857
You fainted.

00:06:42.068 --> 00:06:45.988
It appears the spirit of the Crown Prince took hold of you.

00:06:47.865 --> 00:06:51.077
He used your body to hide his own.

00:06:53.037 --> 00:06:53.955
Then

00:06:54.831 --> 00:06:56.707
Is he still attached to me?

00:06:56.791 --> 00:06:58.292
I do not know.

00:07:00.044 --> 00:07:01.254
What do you mean?

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:07.009
I injured my eyes in the Realm of Gwi, so I cannot see spirits.

00:07:09.846 --> 00:07:11.514
Get some rest for now.

00:07:12.432 --> 00:07:14.684
I will look for the Crown Prince's body.

00:07:16.185 --> 00:07:17.395
There is no need.

00:07:20.022 --> 00:07:21.482
What do you mean?

00:07:22.442 --> 00:07:24.569
Even if you find the body and banish the spirit,

00:07:24.652 --> 00:07:27.530
He will spare neither you nor me.

00:07:29.365 --> 00:07:31.200
The man killed his own son.

00:07:34.662 --> 00:07:35.997
Killed his own son?

00:07:40.793 --> 00:07:44.380
<i>The rice in his mouth had turned black.</i>

00:07:46.591 --> 00:07:48.468
He was poisoned.

00:07:53.681 --> 00:07:55.558
To avoid ending up like the Crown Prince,

00:07:57.143 --> 00:08:00.062
We must prove that the incidents 30 years ago,

00:08:00.146 --> 00:08:03.024
Thought to be the spirit's curse, were all Father's doing.

00:08:04.066 --> 00:08:07.111
Before he kills more people.

00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:10.323
I sent the soldiers and carried out your command.

00:08:10.823 --> 00:08:15.203
However, it appears some of them released women and children,

00:08:15.286 --> 00:08:16.913
Allowing them to escape.

00:08:23.586 --> 00:08:27.381
Are those who released the villagers still there?

00:08:28.299 --> 00:08:29.884
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:08:30.384 --> 00:08:34.138
Then seize them, and in front of the other soldiers

00:08:36.682 --> 00:08:38.142
Behead them.

00:08:44.273 --> 00:08:45.483
I suppose

00:08:46.275 --> 00:08:49.320
I will have to meet the spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:08:50.488 --> 00:08:51.906
What do you mean?

00:08:51.989 --> 00:08:56.702
I must ask him myself how he came to know of Father's sins.

00:08:58.079 --> 00:08:59.705
He may be asking for my help

00:09:00.373 --> 00:09:02.708
So he can ease his resentment.

00:09:02.792 --> 00:09:03.751
Princess,

00:09:04.418 --> 00:09:06.546
He is already an ak-gwi who has killed people.

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.756
Forget about it.

00:09:09.298 --> 00:09:10.424
Just make this.

00:09:14.095 --> 00:09:15.763
What is this?

00:09:15.846 --> 00:09:20.810
A ward to keep the spirit of the Crown Prince from clinging to you.

00:09:38.286 --> 00:09:39.912
It must be very frustrating

00:09:40.955 --> 00:09:42.498
Not being able to see well.

00:09:44.584 --> 00:09:45.793
There is one good thing.

00:09:47.211 --> 00:09:50.506
For the first time in my life, I see no spirits or gwi-mae at all.

00:09:51.424 --> 00:09:53.593
So I find it nice.

00:10:00.558 --> 00:10:01.851
Then do you wish to

00:10:03.644 --> 00:10:05.646
Go on living like this?

00:10:07.565 --> 00:10:08.858
Even if you can barely see?

00:10:11.652 --> 00:10:13.571
Well, whatever my wishes may be,

00:10:14.530 --> 00:10:17.658
I must regain my sight so we can find the spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:10:18.993 --> 00:10:20.953
Only then will we both survive.

00:10:44.352 --> 00:10:46.437
What are you doing?

00:10:48.397 --> 00:10:50.316
I am checking if the spirit of the Crown Prince

00:10:50.900 --> 00:10:53.152
Has secretly clung to you.

00:10:54.987 --> 00:10:57.073
But now that I can barely see,

00:10:57.156 --> 00:10:59.241
I could never tell.

00:11:00.159 --> 00:11:01.452
Good grief.

00:11:09.001 --> 00:11:10.753
About your sight

00:11:13.255 --> 00:11:16.342
How can you regain it?

00:11:16.425 --> 00:11:19.470
I must find the damn shaman who got in my way.

00:11:21.305 --> 00:11:24.058
Whoever wants the King dead must be keeping that shaman.

00:11:27.561 --> 00:11:29.271
Does anyone come to mind?

00:11:37.738 --> 00:11:40.491
What brings you here?

00:11:41.158 --> 00:11:42.827
I have something to ask you.

00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:44.912
Have you held a shamanic ritual lately?

00:11:45.413 --> 00:11:46.706
A shamanic ritual?

00:11:47.206 --> 00:11:51.168
I believe you summoned a shaman when Prince Yeongan collapsed.

00:11:51.669 --> 00:11:53.421
Where is that shaman?

00:11:53.504 --> 00:11:57.049
You came to see me just to ask that?

00:11:57.633 --> 00:12:01.095
After what you did to me,

00:12:02.596 --> 00:12:04.974
You still dare to stand before me.

00:12:07.226 --> 00:12:08.436
Your Majesty.

00:12:21.282 --> 00:12:22.533
More importantly

00:12:26.662 --> 00:12:31.292
That must be the feng shui master His Majesty brought in.

00:12:31.375 --> 00:12:33.544
Why have you brought him here?

00:12:34.044 --> 00:12:37.006
He is inspecting the palace at His Majesty's command.

00:12:37.089 --> 00:12:39.967
- So the Queen Dowager's residence-- - You speak nothing but lies.

00:12:40.634 --> 00:12:44.346
I know he has been up to something strange.

00:12:46.640 --> 00:12:48.893
Say it yourself.

00:12:48.976 --> 00:12:50.311
Is there still

00:12:51.145 --> 00:12:54.982
A spirit in the palace that preys upon the royal bloodline?

00:12:55.065 --> 00:12:56.150
A spirit in the palace?

00:12:56.233 --> 00:12:58.194
If Uncle were to hear this, he would laugh.

00:12:58.277 --> 00:12:59.862
What did you just say?!

00:13:01.530 --> 00:13:03.574
Whether it was the work of a spirit or not,

00:13:03.657 --> 00:13:06.994
It is a relief that His Majesty has recovered, is it not?

00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:10.247
Especially when pestilence spreads across the land.

00:13:10.331 --> 00:13:13.501
Princess, have you heard as well?

00:13:13.584 --> 00:13:18.547
His Majesty sent soldiers to where the pestilence had broken out.

00:13:18.631 --> 00:13:19.799
And then

00:13:22.760 --> 00:13:24.762
He had everyone put to death.

00:13:32.394 --> 00:13:35.648
Children and elders alike, every last one.

00:13:46.492 --> 00:13:47.952
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

00:13:49.745 --> 00:13:51.247
<i>A living ak-gwi.</i>

00:13:53.374 --> 00:13:57.336
<i>They say it was the first thing</i> <i>His Majesty did upon waking.</i>

00:13:59.004 --> 00:14:00.673
Mother!

00:14:03.300 --> 00:14:07.263
Mother, please wake up.

00:14:07.763 --> 00:14:09.974
<i>Father killed me.</i>

00:14:10.057 --> 00:14:12.810
<i>You know the secret.</i> <i>He will kill everyone.</i>

00:14:12.893 --> 00:14:15.104
<i>You are next. Father killed me.</i>

00:14:15.187 --> 00:14:17.022
<i>You are next.</i>

00:14:20.401 --> 00:14:22.528
What do you think you are doing to the Princess?

00:14:26.699 --> 00:14:29.034
There was a centipede as big as a snake.

00:14:30.035 --> 00:14:31.954
Perhaps the vermin are gathering here.

00:14:36.250 --> 00:14:40.170
Uncle, did you come here to report this matter to Her Majesty?

00:14:40.254 --> 00:14:43.507
Why would I concern myself with it when I hold no office?

00:14:44.049 --> 00:14:46.343
His Majesty has issued an edict

00:14:46.427 --> 00:14:49.346
That he will appoint my eldest son as Crown Prince,

00:14:49.430 --> 00:14:51.432
So I came to pay my respects

00:14:53.642 --> 00:14:55.728
To Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:15:02.860 --> 00:15:07.197
<i>Bring Prince Iksang's son, Prince Inha,</i> <i>into the palace to learn court etiquette</i>

00:15:07.740 --> 00:15:11.201
<i>and hold the Crown Prince investiture</i> <i>as soon as possible.</i>

00:15:12.286 --> 00:15:14.121
<i>With the land in turmoil,</i>

00:15:14.747 --> 00:15:17.291
<i>we cannot leave the East Palace vacant</i> <i>any longer.</i>

00:15:18.167 --> 00:15:23.172
<i>I will take Prince Inha as my son</i> <i>and seat him upon the throne.</i>

00:15:25.341 --> 00:15:26.759
<i>He will kill me.</i>

00:15:27.801 --> 00:15:29.136
<i>He will.</i>

00:15:30.012 --> 00:15:31.764
<i>He is a man</i>

00:15:32.556 --> 00:15:34.600
<i>who killed his own son.</i>

00:15:35.309 --> 00:15:36.560
<i>That would mean</i>

00:15:37.311 --> 00:15:38.562
<i>even I could be</i>

00:15:39.688 --> 00:15:43.025
RABBIT

00:15:48.822 --> 00:15:51.200
What are you doing?

00:15:51.742 --> 00:15:53.202
Compose yourself.

00:15:53.285 --> 00:15:56.372
Dark thoughts will cause your mind to collapse.

00:15:56.872 --> 00:15:59.375
What if a spirit slips in through that crack?

00:16:01.627 --> 00:16:03.003
Just set the ward.

00:16:03.921 --> 00:16:06.715
I can barely see, so you must do it all.

00:16:17.059 --> 00:16:18.185
Lower.

00:16:18.727 --> 00:16:20.646
- Place it lower. - I know.

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:23.065
It is already set low.

00:16:23.565 --> 00:16:24.566
RABBIT

00:16:24.650 --> 00:16:27.569
- I said-- - I will let this go as you can barely see.

00:16:36.203 --> 00:16:40.207
But why the "rabbit" sign? And upside down at that.

00:16:40.290 --> 00:16:42.626
The Crown Prince was born in the Year of the Rabbit.

00:16:43.127 --> 00:16:44.878
With his sign upside down,

00:16:45.963 --> 00:16:49.049
His soul cannot pass through here without a body.

00:16:51.760 --> 00:16:53.470
So be careful

00:16:54.304 --> 00:16:56.807
Unless you want him to take your body.

00:16:57.307 --> 00:16:59.309
I had no other choice back then.

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:03.856
After hearing that your father killed his own child,

00:17:04.356 --> 00:17:06.442
How could you possibly remain sane?

00:17:10.738 --> 00:17:12.322
I will say this again.

00:17:12.823 --> 00:17:15.409
You must compose yourself.

00:17:18.537 --> 00:17:22.750
If you cannot, remain close to someone you can rely on.

00:17:31.884 --> 00:17:33.052
There is someone.

00:17:33.135 --> 00:17:35.012
Someone I can rely on.

00:17:44.271 --> 00:17:45.606
Saeng-gang.

00:17:46.940 --> 00:17:48.192
Where are you headed?

00:17:48.275 --> 00:17:49.735
Have you been well?

00:17:50.235 --> 00:17:52.738
- You do not look so good. - Good for her.

00:17:53.238 --> 00:17:55.240
You are leaving the palace?

00:17:55.824 --> 00:17:58.577
I came to care for Prince Yeongan,

00:17:58.660 --> 00:18:00.662
Yet I cannot do that anymore, can I?

00:18:01.163 --> 00:18:05.209
With you and Gu-cheon here, His Majesty should be safe.

00:18:05.793 --> 00:18:06.627
However,

00:18:07.127 --> 00:18:09.379
The matter of the late Crown Prince

00:18:10.047 --> 00:18:13.050
It is hard to believe he has become a spirit, is it not?

00:18:18.806 --> 00:18:22.851
This palace is truly a frightening place.

00:18:23.435 --> 00:18:25.604
It does not suit an old woman like me.

00:18:29.024 --> 00:18:30.734
He looks just like a corpse.

00:18:30.818 --> 00:18:32.611
He cannot even eat or speak.

00:18:33.112 --> 00:18:36.782
A shaman who lost their presiding deity is as good as dead.

00:18:36.865 --> 00:18:38.283
Good heavens, let us get going.

00:20:03.035 --> 00:20:04.661
Take me in.

00:20:27.434 --> 00:20:30.479
I shall be your new presiding deity.

00:20:31.021 --> 00:20:34.358
Your Highness, the Crown Prince!

00:20:56.588 --> 00:20:58.006
What happened?

00:21:01.093 --> 00:21:02.052
My eyes.

00:21:03.136 --> 00:21:05.097
I can no longer see at all.

00:21:09.142 --> 00:21:10.727
That damn shaman

00:21:11.561 --> 00:21:14.022
Must have burned the object that cursed my eyes.

00:21:14.106 --> 00:21:16.692
Perhaps he has already taken in a new presiding deity.

00:21:22.823 --> 00:21:24.866
Then what do we do now?

00:21:25.492 --> 00:21:27.869
Now that I cannot see spirits,

00:21:29.371 --> 00:21:31.206
It is all over.

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:35.294
Is there any way to regain your sight?

00:21:40.132 --> 00:21:43.385
There is one way, but it is far too dangerous.

00:21:44.803 --> 00:21:46.054
Why is that?

00:21:46.138 --> 00:21:49.016
It means disturbing what must not be disturbed.

00:21:57.232 --> 00:21:59.484
But if that is the only way

00:22:01.862 --> 00:22:02.696
We must do it.

00:22:02.779 --> 00:22:03.864
No.

00:22:04.573 --> 00:22:07.492
I would rather flee the palace than do that.

00:22:08.952 --> 00:22:11.705
As long as I stay hidden, I will survive.

00:22:12.664 --> 00:22:14.833
You cannot even see. Where would you go?

00:22:19.254 --> 00:22:20.797
Since it has come to this,

00:22:21.673 --> 00:22:23.425
You should flee the palace with me.

00:22:23.508 --> 00:22:27.054
The moment we flee, His Majesty will send troops to kill us.

00:22:27.637 --> 00:22:31.099
And I do not wish to leave the palace again for no fault of my own,

00:22:31.183 --> 00:22:32.809
As I did as a child.

00:22:33.810 --> 00:22:37.397
If you will not help me, I shall find the Crown Prince myself.

00:22:37.481 --> 00:22:40.359
I will find a way to save us both, even alone.

00:22:40.442 --> 00:22:42.110
How would you do that alone?

00:22:45.113 --> 00:22:47.157
If the Crown Prince spirit comes near,

00:22:48.575 --> 00:22:49.659
I will not stop it.

00:22:50.535 --> 00:22:53.038
Do you understand how dangerous that is?

00:22:53.872 --> 00:22:55.999
- If it takes your body-- - That will not happen.

00:22:56.708 --> 00:23:00.545
His Majesty's sins must be proven no matter what.

00:23:06.968 --> 00:23:08.762
You have truly lost your mind.

00:23:21.441 --> 00:23:24.569
Did you see the look on the Princess's face?

00:23:25.487 --> 00:23:28.198
Look on her face?

00:23:30.492 --> 00:23:35.580
Did she not look as if she were tormented by a spirit?

00:23:36.081 --> 00:23:39.501
Could the spirit of the Most Favored Lady of the Court

00:23:39.584 --> 00:23:42.546
Still remain in the palace?

00:23:42.629 --> 00:23:43.755
No.

00:23:44.256 --> 00:23:49.136
That man called Gu-cheon surely banished it.

00:23:49.219 --> 00:23:51.012
I feel lighter.

00:23:51.096 --> 00:23:53.974
It means the resentment toward me is gone.

00:23:54.474 --> 00:23:56.643
Yet Prince Yeongan is dead,

00:23:56.726 --> 00:23:59.187
And both His Majesty and the Princess have fallen ill.

00:24:04.484 --> 00:24:10.198
Could it be another spirit that is after the King?

00:24:14.870 --> 00:24:15.912
Your Majesty.

00:24:15.996 --> 00:24:20.083
It was my shame that blinded me.

00:24:20.167 --> 00:24:23.378
Of all the late King's sons,

00:24:23.462 --> 00:24:26.047
Why was the present King the only one to survive?

00:24:26.131 --> 00:24:29.885
How did he survive the curse alone?

00:24:31.803 --> 00:24:32.846
<i>Yes.</i>

00:24:33.346 --> 00:24:35.515
<i>There must be another reason.</i>

00:24:36.433 --> 00:24:40.979
<i>There was a royal physician who examined</i> <i>the dead Princes 30 years ago.</i>

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:42.981
<i>Find him.</i>

00:24:49.571 --> 00:24:51.239
He is dead?

00:24:51.740 --> 00:24:53.283
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:24:53.783 --> 00:24:57.704
I traced the royal physician who attended the Princes 30 years ago.

00:24:58.538 --> 00:25:00.373
A few years after,

00:25:00.457 --> 00:25:03.460
He suddenly coughed up dark blood and died.

00:25:03.960 --> 00:25:07.631
Those are the same symptoms the dead Princes had, are they not?

00:25:10.258 --> 00:25:13.970
Then it was not a spirit

00:25:14.763 --> 00:25:17.140
That preyed upon the King's bloodline.

00:25:19.976 --> 00:25:20.977
Pardon?

00:25:24.523 --> 00:25:27.692
Where is the son of Prince Iksang right now?

00:25:32.364 --> 00:25:35.283
Prince Inha!

00:25:37.285 --> 00:25:38.537
Summon the physician.

00:25:38.620 --> 00:25:39.496
Yes, ma'am!

00:25:51.466 --> 00:25:53.009
What is it at this late hour?

00:25:53.093 --> 00:25:55.720
Her Majesty summons you, Your Highness.

00:25:55.804 --> 00:25:57.430
For what reason?

00:25:58.306 --> 00:26:00.267
Prince Inha has collapsed.

00:26:02.519 --> 00:26:04.646
Then why have I been summoned?

00:26:05.313 --> 00:26:06.690
In that chamber,

00:26:07.482 --> 00:26:08.900
We found a refreshment box.

00:26:12.362 --> 00:26:16.700
It bears the same pattern as the one you once brought to Her Majesty.

00:26:17.993 --> 00:26:22.747
Her Majesty says it appears he collapsed after eating what was in that box.

00:26:28.795 --> 00:26:30.005
Your Highness.

00:26:43.143 --> 00:26:44.144
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:26:46.146 --> 00:26:47.355
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:26:47.439 --> 00:26:48.773
Saeng-gang!

00:26:49.858 --> 00:26:50.900
Saeng-gang.

00:26:53.069 --> 00:26:55.530
What is wrong with you? Have you come to your senses?

00:26:57.949 --> 00:26:59.576
Why am I here?

00:26:59.659 --> 00:27:01.077
I should be asking you that.

00:27:01.578 --> 00:27:04.247
You appeared out of nowhere and just stood there.

00:27:04.331 --> 00:27:06.166
I should take my leave now.

00:27:09.919 --> 00:27:13.131
What on earth is going on? You can tell me.

00:27:18.094 --> 00:27:19.304
Grandmother.

00:27:21.222 --> 00:27:22.599
Father

00:27:24.684 --> 00:27:26.645
Intends to begin again.

00:27:28.063 --> 00:27:28.897
To become

00:27:29.731 --> 00:27:31.733
The pond spirit himself.

00:27:32.692 --> 00:27:34.235
The pond spirit?

00:27:34.736 --> 00:27:37.155
The one who killed his brothers 30 years ago

00:27:39.658 --> 00:27:40.700
Was Father.

00:27:41.618 --> 00:27:42.452
What

00:27:44.371 --> 00:27:46.998
- What are you talking-- - But he means to do it again.

00:27:48.041 --> 00:27:49.959
He intends to kill someone.

00:27:51.169 --> 00:27:54.297
He summoned Prince Iksang's son to the palace and poisoned him.

00:27:58.885 --> 00:28:00.136
That cannot be.

00:28:00.220 --> 00:28:03.306
There was a lotus-patterned refreshment box in his quarters.

00:28:03.390 --> 00:28:04.724
Mother also died

00:28:06.643 --> 00:28:09.479
After eating what was in that box.

00:28:10.689 --> 00:28:12.565
- That is impossible. - No!

00:28:13.608 --> 00:28:17.821
Grandmother, you noticed something strange about Father as well, did you not?

00:28:17.904 --> 00:28:20.073
If you know anything, please tell me.

00:28:20.156 --> 00:28:22.242
Father must be stopped no matter what.

00:28:22.325 --> 00:28:23.535
If there is no other way,

00:28:24.869 --> 00:28:26.996
We must have him step down from the throne.

00:28:46.266 --> 00:28:48.101
Forgive me.

00:28:49.185 --> 00:28:50.353
<i>Disappeared?</i>

00:28:50.437 --> 00:28:51.563
What?

00:28:51.646 --> 00:28:53.398
Was she not here to see you?

00:28:53.481 --> 00:28:55.442
Then where did she go?

00:28:56.651 --> 00:28:58.486
Tell me again from the beginning.

00:29:03.825 --> 00:29:09.205
The moment she heard from Lady Jang that Prince Inha had collapsed,

00:29:09.289 --> 00:29:13.293
She pushed past the people there and went off somewhere.

00:29:13.376 --> 00:29:15.044
They say she was not herself,

00:29:15.545 --> 00:29:19.174
As if she had lost her mind.

00:29:24.053 --> 00:29:26.139
She has collapsed inside.

00:29:27.766 --> 00:29:30.393
Do you know where the Princess might be?

00:29:30.894 --> 00:29:32.353
<i>I do.</i>

00:29:32.937 --> 00:29:35.190
<i>A place where there is someone</i> <i>she can rely on.</i>

00:29:39.527 --> 00:29:42.489
But does that man, Gu-cheon,

00:29:43.531 --> 00:29:45.617
Know about this?

00:29:48.244 --> 00:29:49.412
No, he does not.

00:29:50.455 --> 00:29:52.457
Only I, who can hear the voice of spirits,

00:29:54.042 --> 00:29:55.502
Know about this.

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:02.091
That is a lie.

00:30:07.680 --> 00:30:08.890
Pardon?

00:30:11.184 --> 00:30:12.560
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:30:17.398 --> 00:30:18.733
Mother?

00:30:42.549 --> 00:30:43.967
Protective sutras

00:30:45.009 --> 00:30:47.595
<i>Stay away from her.</i>

00:30:53.184 --> 00:30:55.186
<i>Stay away from her. Spirits do not exist.</i>

00:30:55.270 --> 00:30:59.399
<i>One day, everyone will know</i> <i>that you are the pond spirit.</i>

00:31:00.358 --> 00:31:03.278
It seems your mother is outside.

00:31:03.361 --> 00:31:07.657
When will she ever stop following me? This is why I did not want to come here.

00:31:11.828 --> 00:31:12.662
Are there

00:31:13.538 --> 00:31:15.623
Other spirits outside as well?

00:31:17.500 --> 00:31:18.668
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:31:19.836 --> 00:31:22.005
<i>Stay away from her.</i>

00:31:29.012 --> 00:31:31.931
The serpent's cast skin killed the dragon's child.

00:31:32.015 --> 00:31:34.726
The serpent's cast skin killed the dragon's child.

00:31:37.020 --> 00:31:39.355
<i>It is dangerous, Saeng-gang.</i>

00:31:39.439 --> 00:31:42.275
Your Grace.

00:31:42.358 --> 00:31:45.445
No one can find out about this poison.

00:31:50.950 --> 00:31:52.118
When I was a child

00:31:54.203 --> 00:31:57.540
You always came to see Mother and me after we were cast out of the palace.

00:31:58.499 --> 00:32:02.754
You would bring food wrapped in cloths and boxes.

00:32:14.849 --> 00:32:16.809
The one who poisoned Mother

00:32:19.020 --> 00:32:20.063
Was it you?

00:32:22.899 --> 00:32:23.775
That is right.

00:32:23.858 --> 00:32:25.109
You just

00:32:25.610 --> 00:32:27.111
Drank the same thing.

00:32:29.072 --> 00:32:31.199
Since it was a weaker poison,

00:32:31.824 --> 00:32:34.285
You will not die as the Princes did.

00:32:40.959 --> 00:32:43.711
You will only lie there like a living corpse,

00:32:43.795 --> 00:32:46.381
Unable to speak for the rest of your life.

00:32:51.052 --> 00:32:52.637
<i>Grandmother,</i>

00:32:53.179 --> 00:32:55.348
<i>you were the pond spirit.</i>

00:32:58.726 --> 00:33:00.520
- Your Highness! - Your Highness!

00:33:00.603 --> 00:33:01.854
Your Highness!

00:33:01.938 --> 00:33:03.773
- Your Highness! - Bring a stretcher!

00:33:03.856 --> 00:33:05.525
Summon the physician now!

00:33:06.025 --> 00:33:08.444
- Your Highness! - Your Highness!

00:33:08.528 --> 00:33:10.363
Your Highness!

00:33:21.749 --> 00:33:23.584
I cannot believe he suddenly died

00:33:24.210 --> 00:33:25.670
While riding a horse.

00:33:26.254 --> 00:33:28.381
He had always been frail.

00:33:31.092 --> 00:33:32.885
The Most Favored Lady of the Court,

00:33:32.969 --> 00:33:34.929
Who vowed to end the royal bloodline, died,

00:33:35.596 --> 00:33:39.392
And shortly after, the Crown Prince was gone as well.

00:33:42.020 --> 00:33:44.188
What a wonderful coincidence.

00:33:45.189 --> 00:33:46.774
I have brought it, Your Grace.

00:33:47.525 --> 00:33:50.653
No one can find out about this poison.

00:33:53.781 --> 00:33:55.742
<i>We must make people believe</i>

00:33:55.825 --> 00:34:00.038
<i>the Princes died from a curse of a spirit.</i>

00:34:02.206 --> 00:34:06.252
<i>The pond spirit who cursed</i> <i>the royal family and died.</i>

00:34:06.335 --> 00:34:07.670
Your Majesty.

00:34:09.505 --> 00:34:11.632
<i>The Queen,</i>

00:34:12.216 --> 00:34:14.927
<i>who turned the Most Favored Lady</i> <i>of the Court into a spirit,</i>

00:34:15.511 --> 00:34:17.597
<i>must be blamed for all of this.</i>

00:34:18.222 --> 00:34:21.893
THE SERPENT'S CAST SKIN KILLED THE DRAGON'S CHILD

00:34:21.976 --> 00:34:25.646
One of you must have defiled the royal house.

00:34:33.321 --> 00:34:34.322
<i>And</i>

00:34:35.281 --> 00:34:37.450
<i>once all the other Princes are dead</i>

00:34:39.952 --> 00:34:41.287
<i>my son</i>

00:34:42.622 --> 00:34:44.165
<i>will become the Crown Prince.</i>

00:34:50.880 --> 00:34:52.882
<i>I must remove those</i>

00:34:53.800 --> 00:34:55.885
<i>who might reveal the secret.</i>

00:34:56.511 --> 00:35:01.057
<i>Anyone who would harm my son.</i>

00:35:02.934 --> 00:35:05.478
<i>So is that why you killed Mother as well?</i>

00:35:06.062 --> 00:35:09.774
Simply because she later learned Father's secret?

00:35:09.857 --> 00:35:11.150
Later?

00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:15.363
Your mother was in on this with me from the beginning.

00:35:34.173 --> 00:35:38.386
<i>If not, how could your lowborn mother,</i> <i>a mere court lady of the Saenggwabang,</i>

00:35:38.469 --> 00:35:41.013
<i>have risen to the rank of consort?</i>

00:35:51.941 --> 00:35:55.945
It is a throne your father and your mother helped me build.

00:35:56.028 --> 00:35:57.655
You, too,

00:35:58.489 --> 00:36:00.575
Are the product of that sin.

00:36:11.961 --> 00:36:13.754
<i>He must be stopped.</i>

00:36:15.965 --> 00:36:17.633
<i>We must prevent</i>

00:36:18.301 --> 00:36:19.719
<i>any further sacrifice.</i>

00:36:21.304 --> 00:36:23.848
<i>There was never any spirit to begin with.</i>

00:36:24.724 --> 00:36:27.518
<i>There is no spirit that seeks to wipe out</i> <i>the royal bloodline.</i>

00:36:29.103 --> 00:36:30.188
<i>The King.</i>

00:36:30.688 --> 00:36:32.857
<i>He is the living ak-gwi.</i>

00:36:32.940 --> 00:36:34.859
<i>The King must be stopped.</i>

00:37:22.657 --> 00:37:24.951
Saeng-gang.

00:37:33.167 --> 00:37:35.670
So this is where spirits came through.

00:37:36.170 --> 00:37:39.340
- Where has the Princess gone? - I do not know.

00:37:39.840 --> 00:37:42.093
More importantly, you should

00:38:05.825 --> 00:38:07.410
She threw away the ward.

00:38:09.912 --> 00:38:11.372
It has collapsed.

00:38:23.342 --> 00:38:26.220
What sin did you commit to fear spirits so greatly

00:38:26.846 --> 00:38:30.474
That you placed protective sutras on every door?

00:38:33.769 --> 00:38:35.479
Answer me!

00:38:35.563 --> 00:38:36.772
What have you done

00:38:36.856 --> 00:38:39.859
That your granddaughter lost her mind and gave herself to a spirit?

00:38:55.124 --> 00:38:56.625
What is that?

00:38:57.376 --> 00:38:58.252
A straw effigy.

00:38:58.836 --> 00:39:01.255
It will bear the ill fortune in my stead.

00:39:01.339 --> 00:39:02.840
In your stead? What does it--

00:39:02.923 --> 00:39:04.467
Hang this

00:39:05.760 --> 00:39:07.762
Exactly where I told you.

00:39:08.679 --> 00:39:11.098
And what will you do in the meantime?

00:39:11.974 --> 00:39:13.476
I will go save the Princess.

00:39:15.811 --> 00:39:18.814
I warned her not to let the spirit take hold of her.

00:39:19.732 --> 00:39:21.650
How foolish and pathetic.

00:39:24.779 --> 00:39:25.613
Here.

00:39:45.299 --> 00:39:47.218
So it comes to this.

00:39:47.718 --> 00:39:50.137
Damn my fate.

00:41:33.782 --> 00:41:34.783
RABBIT

00:43:33.485 --> 00:43:34.778
Please help her.

00:43:38.198 --> 00:43:39.491
My Saeng-gang.

00:43:40.826 --> 00:43:42.286
Please help her.

00:43:44.371 --> 00:43:46.290
Please save my daughter.

00:43:49.084 --> 00:43:50.294
My sins

00:43:51.879 --> 00:43:53.005
Put

00:43:53.505 --> 00:43:55.424
Put my daughter in danger.

00:43:55.507 --> 00:43:56.634
Your Highness.

00:44:02.973 --> 00:44:04.683
<i>Please save her</i>

00:44:07.019 --> 00:44:08.437
<i>from that ak-gwi.</i>

00:44:19.490 --> 00:44:20.949
<i>Princess!</i>

00:44:25.537 --> 00:44:26.914
<i>Get a hold of yourself.</i>

00:44:29.500 --> 00:44:32.378
To fight the spirit of the Crown Prince,

00:44:32.461 --> 00:44:34.463
You must first regain your senses.

00:44:34.963 --> 00:44:36.048
Do you hear me?

00:47:56.957 --> 00:48:00.210
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang

